summary:
Leapmotor is expanding globally through a partnership with Stellantis NV (NYSE
), the automaker behind Chrysler and Jeep. Co-founder Zhu Jiangming expects the collaboration to accelerate Leapmotor&#39;s EV reach internationally. Despite delivering fewer vehicles than BYD (OTC
) and Tesla (NASDAQ: TSLA), Leapmotor&#39;s technological edge and affordable pricing have attracted Stellantis.
